Govpress MCP Data Notice

This repository contains machine-converted derivatives of Korean government policy briefing press releases.

Source

- Primary source: korea.kr policy briefing API payloads and attached press-release files retrieved through `apis.data.go.kr`
- Covered period in this Phase 1 backfill: `2021-04-18 ~ 2026-04-18`
- Stored artifacts:
